<h2>🔑 Your 2FA backup codes</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
<p>Here are your backup codes for two-factor authentication. Store them somewhere safe:</p>

<div class="badge-grid">
  {{#each codes}}
    <span class="badge">{{this}}</span>
  {{/each}}
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>⚠️ Important</strong></p>
  <p style="margin: 0;">
    Each code works once. Keep them private, and use one to sign in if you ever lose access to your authenticator app.
  </p>
</div>
